<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="//spoqa.github.io/spoqa-han-sans/css/SpoqaHanSans-kr.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://rsms.me/inter/inter.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Spoqa Han Sans', sans-serif
    }

    h1 {
      padding: 7% 0 0 0;
      /* margin-top: -8%; */
      margin-top: 80px;
      font-size: 125px;
      font-weight: 800;
      /* font-size: 22px; */
      color: #000;
    }

    strong {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 150px;
      /* margin-left: 8%; */
      font-size: 90px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #111;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 80px;
      font-size: 22px;
      /* color: #888888; */
      /* color: #666; */
      /* color: #222; */
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    p + p {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    button {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-top: 60px;
      margin-left: 8%;
      /* background-color: #1e3428; */
      background-color: #003748;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .global-cursor {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      position: fixed;
      opacity: 1;
      -webkit-transition: opacity .5s cubic-bezier(1,.15,.25,1);
      transition: opacity .5s cubic-bezier(1,.15,.25,1);
      z-index: 998;
      pointer-events: none
    }

    .global-cursor .cursor-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 998;
      pointer-events: none
    }

    .cursor-dot {      
      display: block;
      width: 8rem;
      height: 8rem;
      border-radius: 4rem;
      background: #ff2828;
      position: absolute;
      -webkit-transform-origin: center center;
      transform-origin: center center;
      -webkit-transform: scale(.25);
      transform: scale(.25);
      will-change: transform;
      -webkit-transition: background-color 1.5s cubic-bezier(1,.15,.25,1)!important;
      transition: background-color 1.5s cubic-bezier(1,.15,.25,1)!important
    }

    .Test {
      display: flex;
      height: 100%;
      padding-left: 8%;
      /* align-items: center; */
      /* justify-content: center; */
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    img {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8%;
      right: 6%;
    }

    a {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 15px;
      right: 15px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="Test">
    <h1>Font lightening</h1>
    <!-- <strong>Drag &amp; Drop Files Here</strong> -->
    <p>폰트 파일을 드래그 & 드롭 또는 아무 화면을 클릭해 폰트를 업로드하세요.</p>
    <p>그 뒤 불필요한 문자를 제거하여 경량화된 서브셋 폰트 파일을 내려받으세요.</p>
    <p>안타깝지만 TTF 파일만 지원합니다 ;(</p>
    <!-- <button type="button">Click<br>Browser files</button> -->
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="/public/image/Untitled-2.svg" alt="">
    <!-- https://www.freepik.com/free-vector/hand-drawn-feather-collection_1133922.htm#page=1&query=feather&position=40 -->
    <a href="http://www.freepik.com" target="_blank">Hand drawn feather designed by Archjoe / Freepik</a>
  </div>
  <div class="global-cursor">

    <div class="cursor-wrapper">
      <span class="cursor-dot" style="transform: matrix(0.25, 0, 0, 0.25, 1576, 350);"></span>
      <span class="cursor-dot" style="transform: matrix(0.2, 0, 0, 0.2, 1576, 350);"></span>
      <span class="cursor-dot" style="transform: matrix(0.15, 0, 0, 0.15, 1576, 350);"></span>
        <span class="cursor-dot" style="transform: matrix(0.1, 0, 0, 0.1, 1576, 350);"></span>
        <span class="cursor-dot" style="transform: matrix(0.05, 0, 0, 0.05, 1576, 350);"></span>
      </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    window.addEventListener('mousemove', cursorHandler);
    function sursorHandler() {
      const cursorDots = document.querySelectorAll('.cursor-dot');
      cursorDots.forEach(function (t, s) {
        TweenLite.to(t, (s + 1) / e.dotsNumber / 7.5, {
          ease: Power1.easeOut,
          x: e.clientPositions.x - e.baseCursorSize / 2,
          y: e.clientPositions.y - e.baseCursorSize / 2
        })
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>

</html>